OL,3,C'Everyone should pay' : Fare evaders
OL,4,Ctargeted by TFL
OL,6,FITV London's political correspondent,
OL,7,FSimon Harris, went to Leyton Station
OL,8,Fto find out how TFL are tackling the
OL,9,Fproblem.
OL,11,FTransport for London (TFL) say they're
OL,12,Fcracking down on fare evaders as
OL,13,Fcommuters criticise the 'disgusting'
OL,14,Fbehaviour.
OL,16,FThe organisation is trying to tackling
OL,17,Fthe issue with an increased presence
OL,18,Fat stations with officers watching
OL,19,Fover barriers as passengers pass
OL,20,Fthrough.
