OL,3,C'Everyone should pay' : Fare evaders
OL,4,Ctargeted by TFL
OL,6,FSome of these fare dodgers use other
OL,7,Fpeople to get through the barriers,
OL,8,Fbarging in behind them after they've
OL,9,Fpaid.
OL,11,FWhilst others, jump over the barriers,
OL,12,Favoiding them altogether.
OL,14,FOne commuter said: "It's disgusting,
OL,15,Fabsolutely disgusting. I mean, I pay
OL,16,Fmy tax and everything, so people
OL,17,Fshould pay. Everyone should pay."
OL,19,F"I've got two mouths to feed, so why
OL,20,Fshould people get free travel if I
OL,21,Fcan't?" said another.
