OL,3,C'Everyone should pay' : Fare evaders
OL,4,Ctargeted by TFL
OL,6,FOne person on their way into the
OL,7,Fstation, added: "I can understand it
OL,8,Fbecause I think life is tough, it's
OL,9,Fvery expensive. So I think young
OL,10,Fpeople struggling.
OL,12,FOne woman said : "It's unfair.
OL,13,FEverybody needs to pay."
OL,15,F"It costs a lot of money to travel.
OL,16,FThese people are trying to ride for
OL,17,Fyou free," said someone else.
