OL,3,C'Everyone should pay' : Fare evaders
OL,4,Ctargeted by TFL
OL,6,FTFL estimates that 3.5% of all
OL,7,Fjourneys on its tubes, trains, trams
OL,8,Fand buses are made by fare dodgers
OL,9,Fwhich equals more than 122 million
OL,10,Fjourneys across the network.
OL,12,FA recent video from Conservative MP,
OL,13,FRobert Jenrick, showed him confronting
OL,14,Ffare dodgers at Stratford Station
OL,15,Fwhich raised further questions about
OL,16,Fwhat the network are doing.
