OL,3,C'Everyone should pay' : Fare evaders
OL,4,Ctargeted by TFL
OL,6,FAt Leyton - one stop down - from where
OL,7,Fthat video was taken, Revenue
OL,8,FProtection Officers backed up by
OL,9,Fenforcement teams have been trying to
OL,10,Fcatch those persistent offenders.
OL,12,F"We have exercises like the one you
OL,13,Fsee here today happening every day
OL,14,Facross the network," said Siwan
OL,15,FHayward, the Director of Security,
OL,16,FPolicing and Enforcement at TFL.
OL,18,F"We're also finding new ways to tackle
OL,19,Fsome of the new forms of fare evasion."
