OL,3,C'Everyone should pay' : Fare evaders
OL,4,Ctargeted by TFL
OL,6,FIn April 2025, TFL released new
OL,7,Fmeasures including a team of dedicated
OL,8,Finvestigators to identify and target
OL,9,Fthe "most persistent and high-impact
OL,10,Foffenders".
OL,12,FBut as well as this, there are now new
OL,13,Fticket barriers across the network
OL,14,Fthat are making it more difficult for
OL,15,Fany offenders to push their way
OL,16,Fthrough and TFL are also speaking to
OL,17,Fsocial media platform TikTok which is
OL,18,Fhome to videos 'glamorising' so called
OL,19,F'bumping'.
