OL,3,C'Everyone should pay' : Fare evaders
OL,4,Ctargeted by TFL
OL,6,FIn 2024, fare dodgers were also taken
OL,7,Fto court with some paying a penalty
OL,8,Ffare of #100.
OL,10,FAt the time of these incidents, one
OL,11,Fofficer says they sometimes have to
OL,12,Fphysically intervene.
OL,14,F"Where people lash out, swing, try to
OL,15,Fuse instruments to, you know, it can
OL,16,Fget pretty volatile and we've given
OL,17,Fparticular training to try and diffuse
OL,18,Fthose situations as well," said X.
OL,20,F"But we do have instances where
OL,21,Fwe...carry people out of the stations."
